---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AffiliateCTA from '../../components/AffiliateCTA.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
import { AFFILIATE_LINKS as affiliates } from '../../config/affiliate-links';

const title = 'AI Website Builders Under $10/Month (2025)';
const description = 'Budget AI website builders compared. Hostinger is cheapest at $2.99. Durable is $15 but has free trial. Here is the breakdown.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold mb-4">CATEGORY</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">AI Website Builders Under $10/Month</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Building on a budget? Here are your options.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Quick Answer</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg">
        <strong>Hostinger at $2.99/month</strong> is the cheapest AI builder with actual features.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Reality:</strong> Most "under $10" options are limited. Consider spending $15-20 for significantly better tools.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <Card title="Hostinger" subtitle="$2.99/mo - Cheapest Option">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Hostinger is by far the cheapest AI builder. Includes hosting, decent templates, and AI generation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong>Pros:</strong> Unbeatable price, includes hosting, fast setup</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Cons:</strong> Basic AI, limited templates, support can be slow
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card title="Consider Spending More" subtitle="$15-20 Gets You Much More">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          For $15-20/month, you get Durable, Framer, or Dorik - significantly better AI and features.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong>Better options:</strong> Durable ($15), Framer ($15), Dorik ($15)</p>
        </Card>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Budget vs Value</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Saving $10/month sounds smart. But is it worth it?
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-4">
          <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Choose budget option if:</strong></p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-2">
            <li>You genuinely can't afford $15/month</li>
            <li>This is a hobby project, not business-critical</li>
            <li>You just need something basic online</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-4">
          <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Spend more if:</strong></p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-2">
            <li>This is for a business that makes money</li>
            <li>You need better AI generation</li>
            <li>You want more templates and features</li>
            <li>You care about design quality</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Pricing Reality Check</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>The math:</strong> Saving $12/month = $144/year. Is $144 worth better AI, templates, and features?
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        For a business website: <strong>No.</strong> The difference in quality and capabilities is worth far more than $12/month.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700">
        For a personal project: <strong>Maybe.</strong> If budget is tight, start cheap and upgrade later.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <AffiliateCTA
        href={affiliates.hostinger.affiliateUrl}
        commission={affiliates.hostinger.commission}
        label="Try Hostinger ($2.99/mo)"
        className="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg inline-block"
      />
      <br class="my-4">
      <AffiliateCTA
        href={affiliates.durable.affiliateUrl}
        commission={affiliates.durable.commission}
        label="Or Try Durable ($15/mo - Better AI)"
        className="bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg inline-block"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
